---
// src/sections/HowItWorks.astro
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white relative">
  <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-full p-6 mb-6 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-full blur-xl opacity-20"></div>
          <i class="ri-route-line text-5xl text-primary relative z-10"></i>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">
          <span class="block">كيف يعمل</span>
          <span class="gradient-text-arabic">وفر لي؟</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-primary to-secondary rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary via-primary to-transparent rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          انضم إلى شبكتنا المتنامية
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 mt-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-full px-6 py-3 shadow-lg border border-primary/20">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-primary">3 خطوات فقط</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="relative mb-8">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 relative z-10">
            ١
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-full blur-xl opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 group-hover:-translate-y-2 w-full">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <i class="ri-file-list-3-line text-primary text-3xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">قدم طلبك</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            أدخل تفاصيل المنتجات التي تحتاجها والكميات المطلوبة بطريقة سهلة ومرنة
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-primary"></i>
              <span>واجهة سهلة الاستخدام</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-primary"></i>
              <span>تفاصيل دقيقة للمنتجات</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="relative mb-8">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 relative z-10">
            ٢
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-primary rounded-full blur-xl opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 group-hover:-translate-y-2 w-full">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/10 to-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <i class="ri-scales-3-line text-secondary text-3xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">قارن العروض</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            احصل على عروض من موردين متعددين وقارن الأسعار والجودة والشروط
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-secondary"></i>
              <span>مقارنة ذكية للأسعار</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-secondary"></i>
              <span>تقييمات الموردين</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="relative mb-8">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 relative z-10">
            ٣
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-full blur-xl opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 group-hover:-translate-y-2 w-full">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <i class="ri-truck-line text-primary text-3xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">استلم طلبك</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            اختر أفضل عرض وأكد الطلب، سيقوم المورد بالتوصيل في الموعد المحدد
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-primary"></i>
              <span>تتبع الطلب مباشرة</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-primary"></i>
              <span>ضمان الجودة والسرعة</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/5 via-secondary/5 to-primary/5 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-primary/10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">انضم إلى شبكتنا المتنامية</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          كن جزءاً من ثورة تجارة الجملة الغذائية واستفد من منصة تقنية متطورة تضعك في المقدمة
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-full px-6 py-3 shadow-lg border border-primary/20">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-primary">✓ أسعار تنافسية</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-full px-6 py-3 shadow-lg border border-secondary/20">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-secondary">✓ توصيل سريع</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-full px-6 py-3 shadow-lg border border-primary/20">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-primary">✓ دعم 24/7</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button
          onclick="document.getElementById('interest-form').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})"
          class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center gap-3 group mt-8"
        >
          <i class="ri-user-add-line text-xl"></i>
          <span>سجل اهتمامك الآن</span>
          <i class="ri-arrow-left-line group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 